36
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,240
Didn't we agree to help each other?

37
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,480
Have you done anything helpful?

38
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:44,680
A Cha has been busy with medicinal food.

39
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,280
