40
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,800
Medicinal food?

41
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,400
A Cha.

42
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,280
Let me help you.

43
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,600
It's so hot!

44
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,200
Are you okay?

45
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:38,720
I'll get you some medicine.

46
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,000
A Cha.

47
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:42,160
I brought some in my medicine box.

48
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,240
