81
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,400
Does it taste that bad?

82
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,960
(I can't give He Lianyu a chance.)

83
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,000
M-My stomach hurts.

84
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,560
W-What's wrong?
Why does your stomach hurt?

85
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,680
Is it because of my medicine?

86
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,560
It worked right away?

87
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:45,120
